name: ENTRY LOG C-885 「 GEMMA ETERNALIA 」
description:
ENTRY LOG	C-885

" GEMMA ETERNALIA "

EPOCH		5013526025
SECTOR		27A
PLANET		Uraceas 428-B
LOCATION	24.211/66.514

NOTE 01
	It looks like a strange translucent rock with some form of lifeform inside. No sign of threat.

NOTE 02
	Attempt to break open results in no harm to the protective material.

NOTE 03
	It has been more than 300 Years since the last observation. My physical body is still the same age as the time of initial discovery. The existence of this must be kept secret to prevent the wrong hands from using its power to overcome their natural death.

-- ENDLOG
